<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <title>Finance API</title>

    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    <link href="/assets/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- HTML5 shim and Respond.js for IE8 support of HTML5 elements and media queries -->
    <!-- WARNING: Respond.js doesn't work if you view the page via file:// -->
    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
      <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/html5shiv/3.7.2/html5shiv.min.js"></script>
      <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/respond/1.4.2/respond.min.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <main>
            <h1>Finance API</h1>
            <h2>Simple Financial Calculator</h2>
            <p>
                The calculations provide information such as how much money will you have when saving a fixed amount per month,
                or how long will it take to pay off a loan with a fixed interest rate.
            </p>

            <section class="row col-sm-12">
                <h3>GET /api/perMonthRetirementSavings</h3>
                <table class="table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Parameter Name</th>
                            <th>Description</th>
                            <th>Sample Value</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td>years</td>
                            <td>The number of years money is being saved for</td>
                            <td>5</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>perMonth</td>
                            <td>The amount of money being saved per month</td>
                            <td>500</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>interestRate</td>
                            <td>The interest rate</td>
                            <td>0.05</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
                <form action="/results/perMonthRetirementSavings" method="POST" class="form-horizontal" id="retirement-savings">
                    <div class="alert alert-danger hidden" id="error-message"></div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="control-label col-sm-2" for="years">Years</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-10">
                            <input type="text" name="years" id="years" placeholder="Years" class="form-control" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="control-label col-sm-2" for="perMonth">Per Month</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-10">
                            <input type="text" name="perMonth" id="perMonth" placeholder="Per month" class="form-control" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="control-label col-sm-2" for="interestRate">Interest Rate</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-10">
                            <input type="text" name="interestRate" id="interestRate" placeholder="Interest rate" class="form-control" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Submit</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h3>GET /api/investedAmount</h3>
                <table class="table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Parameter Name</th>
                            <th>Description</th>
                            <th>Sample Value</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td>years</td>
                            <td>The number of years investing for</td>
                            <td>10</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>initial</td>
                            <td>The initial investment</td>
                            <td>2000</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>interestRate</td>
                            <td>The interest rate on the investment</td>
                            <td>0.02</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
                <form action="/results/investedAmount" method="POST" class="form-horizontal" id="investment">
                    <div class="alert alert-danger hidden" id="error-message"></div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="control-label col-sm-2" for="investYears">Years</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-10">
                            <input type="text" name="investYears" id="investYears" placeholder="Years" class="form-control" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="control-label col-sm-2" for="initial">Initial Investment</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-10">
                            <input type="text" name="initial" id="initial" placeholder="Initial Investment" class="form-control" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="control-label col-sm-2" for="investedInterestRate">Interest Rate</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-10">
                            <input type="text" name="investedInterestRate" id="investedInterestRate" placeholder="Interest rate" class="form-control" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Submit</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h3>GET /api/loanPayoff</h3>
                <table class="table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Parameter Name</th>
                            <th>Description</th>
                            <th>Sample Value</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td>monthlyAmount</td>
                            <td>The amount of the loan paid off per month</td>
                            <td>250</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>loanAmount</td>
                            <td>The total amount of the loan</td>
                            <td>5000</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>interestRate</td>
                            <td>The interest rate of the loan</td>
                            <td>0.02</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
                <form action="/results/loanPayoff" method="POST" class="form-horizontal" id="loan-payoff">
                    <div class="alert alert-danger hidden" id="error-message"></div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="control-label col-sm-2" for="monthlyAmount">Monthly Amount</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-10">
                            <input type="text" name="monthlyAmount" id="monthlyAmount" placeholder="Monthly amount" class="form-control" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="control-label col-sm-2" for="loanAmount">Loan Amount</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-10">
                            <input type="text" name="loanAmount" id="loanAmount" placeholder="Loan Amount" class="form-control" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="control-label col-sm-2" for="loanInterestRate">Interest Rate</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-10">
                            <input type="text" name="loanInterestRate" id="loanInterestRate" placeholder="Interest rate" class="form-control" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Submit</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>About Jason Ajmo</h2>
                <p>
                    My name is Jason Ajmo. I am a 3/5 Cybersecurity major, with interests in security and web development. In my free time,
                    I enjoy coding, playing video games, and cooking.
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Major: Cybersecurity</li>
                    <li>Favorite song: Ghost Love Score - Nightwish</li>
                    <li>Hope to learn in CS-546: Making webpages more accessible with screenreaders, and things of the sort.</li>
                    <li>Favorite programming languages: C, C++</li>
                    <li>Favorite animal: Dog</li>
                </ul>
            </section>
        </main>
    </div>

